Chinese State Councilor Meets Swiss Businessmen 
State Councilor Wu Yi met today with Peter Spaelti, chairman of
Switzerland-based Winterthur Insurance Company, and his party.
The Winterthur Insurance Company, established in 1875, has now grown as
one of ten largest insurance companies in the world. It has also
established representative offices in Beijing, Tianjin and Shanghai
since getting an access to the Chinese market.
The Swiss visitors are here at the invitation of the China Association
for International Friendly Contact.
